    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美和阿布扎比国家石油公司正在考虑竞购天然气生产商 Santos</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/aramco-adnoc-are-said-to-consider-bids-for-gas-producer-santos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，沙特阿美公司和阿布扎比国家石油公司一直在分别研究对桑托斯有限公司的潜在收购要约，这两家公司成为最新两家对这家澳大利亚生产商的液化天然气资产表现出兴趣的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/aramco-adnoc-are-said-to-consider-bids-for-gas-producer-santos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Saks 所有者在亚马逊的帮助下以 26.5 亿美元的价格收购 Neiman</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/saks-owner-said-near-deal-to-buy-neiman-marcus-for-2-65-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[萨克斯第五大道 (Saks Fifth Avenue) 的所有者将以 26.5 亿美元收购尼曼集团 (Neiman Marcus Group) — 这笔交易将合并美国两大高端百货连锁店，以期在增长放缓的行业中抢占更大的份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/saks-owner-said-near-deal-to-buy-neiman-marcus-for-2-65-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 20:09:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
